{"tid":1798685,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"如果季炳雄今天才落網 - 曾志豪","createTime":"2019-12-26T11:35:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T02:01:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":56,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"eb33df6e95971e9c311f9e335bba1ca7b60c8ed9","tid":1798685,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T11:35:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E8%B1%AA/daily/article/20191226/20831550/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E8%25B1%25AA%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191226%2F20831550%2F&d=xSG8yb8yy9PjQoJ4RYEJZLYQZcr3xUkCoBtK5HAxbhw%3D&h=ae3bd218\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E8%25B1%25AA%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191226%2F20831550%2F&h=c09b1eb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E8%B1%AA/daily/article/20191226/20831550/</a><br />\n<br />\n如果季炳雄今天才落網 - 曾志豪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191226/large/1577267212_363d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191226%2Flarge%2F1577267212_363d.jpg&h=8e1cd32e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n季炳雄被捕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2003年的平安夜，另一個賊王季炳雄落網。<br />\n<br />\n當年警察出動了接近二百個警員圍捕，連王敏德口中的the best of the best的飛虎隊都出動。那年的香港人，覺得目睹了人生難得一次的大陣仗。或者連季炳雄自己也自豪，畢竟要襯托一代賊王的身份，當然也要有一定份量的警力才匹配。<br />\n<br />\n不過，季炳雄這份驕傲，應該在這六個月，消失殆盡。因為二百警力已經不能算是甚麼規模，我們閒閒地一個商場和你shop已經可以引來相應的警力，如果在重點區域，尖咀旺角沙田，那便不單單是警員數目龐大，連裝備也層出不窮。<br />\n<br />\n當年季炳雄才不過引來了飛虎隊，還有甚麼爆炸危險品處理車，再無其他可看之處。今天香港人，水炮車銳武裝甲出巡就當是名車展的大匯演，有甚麼大驚小怪？說句不客氣的話，香港人可是連銳裝裝甲車也曾焚燒過，你季炳雄有試過嗎？<br />\n<br />\n當年捉季炳雄，新聞報導大肆宣揚一個重點：警方無開過一槍，便制服了這批有重火力的極悍惡匪。今天香港，一個小學生可能都已經聞過TG，幾多市民被鷹犬的真槍指嚇過？更何況，鷹犬還真的開過真槍，去槍擊學生。<br />\n<br />\n捉悍匪一槍不開，捉學生暴徒近距離射擊，季炳雄真的應該慶幸，自己早已落網，否則來到今天，警員個個都在電光火石間做出不完美可接受要改善的決定，只怕季炳雄都不能服刑，早就被行刑了。而今天季炳雄如果在監獄放風時，和其他倉友閒聊，也是自慚形穢。「你衰乜？」「襲警。」「你用AK？」「唔係，雷射筆。」「雷明登？」「雷射槍。」無言。「咁你又衰乜？」「我打劫，意圖，未打得成。」「你生不逢時，今時今日，香港金鋪打劫無人拉㗎。」「差人去晒邊？」「拉我地囉。」 <br />\n<br />\n曾志豪<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"65caf39055ee53f5bd4006e859e37f5d81268747","tid":1798685,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T11:35:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">無忘承諾 並肩同行<br />\n民陣元誕大遊行</span><br />\n日期 : 1月1日 (三)<br />\n時間：14:00<br />\n地點：維園中央草坪 ==&gt; 遮打道行人專用區"},{"pid":"1b164facdae8f14300b3c2fd3a4d0536cceac371","tid":1798685,"uid":30592,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T12:42:03.000Z","msg":"靚抽 不過同休班狗搶飯碗都係要拉"},{"pid":"cc7852fc8e2f5929bab1780ffdc598da355f5df9","tid":1798685,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T12:46:58.000Z","msg":"【第拾玖期牆紙】毋懼強權<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1797162/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1797162/page/1</a><br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=xSG8yb8yy9PjQoJ4RYEJZLYQZcr3xUkCoBtK5HAxbhw%3D&h=0f9ec7ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nqcF6Fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnqcF6Fe.jpg&h=44c58009&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c8911f23e14fc60ded44365806b06c8762acfb8","tid":1798685,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b164facdae8f14300b3c2fd3a4d0536cceac371","tid":1798685,"uid":30592,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T12:42:03.000Z","msg":"靚抽 不過同休班狗搶飯碗都係要拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T12:48:58.000Z","msg":"直抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"615894da3d08a2b26deb1979c66ff75a4e0fc787","tid":1798685,"ui